description: The SPDR S&P Emerging Markets Small Cap ETF seeks to provide investment results that, before fees and expenses, correspond generally to the total return performance of the S&P Emerging Markets Under USD2 Billion Index (the “Index”)Seeks to provide exposure to the small capitalization segment of emerging countries included in the S&P Global Broad Market IndexThe selection universe includes emerging country equites within the S&P Global BMI with market capitalizations between $100 million and $2 billion at the time of inclusion
name: SPDR S&P Emerging Markets Small Cap ETF
